.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo

# raw/ contains the immutable source-document PDFs. Content is gitignored
# (too large, and includes copyright-licensed material that must not be
# redistributed). raw/README.md is committed and documents the provenance
# model and auditor access process.
raw/*
!raw/README.md
!raw/*/INGESTED.md

